{"tid":1703710,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[最後直路] 政府話就黎嬴啦.. 頂住呀","createTime":"2019-11-10T11:42:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T18:04:45.000Z","uid":27719,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"296783cef6c8388947df2585778eb665ad759463","tid":1703710,"uid":27719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T11:42:27.000Z","msg":"政府就黎嬴喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />林奠或成大嬴家<br />\n聽日三罷預左搞唔成<br />\n反抗報仇所有野都只係口號, 手足係condom<br />\n之前話等第一滴血仲會有暴動.. 暴動就無喇..單方面比人打就有<br />\n<br />\n今日係淘大 megabox 發現好多人係平行時空, 我自己都係入邊..發覺所有事都好平靜..外間一切事都唔無發生咁..睇TG 先知原來打到七彩<br />\n<br />\n雖然係連登講無乜用.. 如果你有幸睇到依個POST請你地認清事實..唔係講侮氣話..<br />\n政府真係進入最後直路.. 我地已經輸咗<br />\n民記呼籲大家帶下口罩都無乜人做..仲講罷工..永遠都有藉口<br />\n有以前同事WHATSAPP GROUP每日都分享啲曱甴點點點..又好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日罷工就一句聲都無<br />\n<br />\n所以第日比人打懵仔針我都唔會喊..因為真係共業黎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最後想多謝夢中既兄弟曾經一齊作戰..雖知煲底相見之期漸遠 但都see you tomorrow"},{"pid":"62cda4861fae8c3bb87489210dab42487c16a8dc","tid":1703710,"uid":27719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:02:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b4c6fb0d69e964c2cae234c85b95f6fbeb1fb45","tid":1703710,"uid":15193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:10:05.000Z","msg":"搞唔成係預左 工會好多野先岩岩起步<br />\n大家請調整好心態 聽日主要係被動罷工<br />\n最後罷唔成都唔好灰心放負<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe15226f08fe7a89b045bea02f489dc0d67f614a","tid":1703710,"uid":27719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b4c6fb0d69e964c2c